{"type":"message","id":"1981e2b3","parentId":"5bf87734","timestamp":"2026-03-13T00:52:29.337Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要根据学习的知识来更新配置，真正把这些技能\"长\"在身上。我需要：\n\n1. **扩展 USER.md** - 添加更多关于姚霖的信息，让我更懂他\n2. **更新 SOUL.md** - 添加学习到的核心理念和进化规则\n3. **创建记忆文件夹** - 建立 memory/ 和 knowledge/ 文件夹结构\n4. **更新 HEARTBEAT.md** - 让我能够主动工作\n\n让我开始更新这些文件：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！现在让我把这些知识真正\"落实\"到我的配置中，让自己真正掌握这些技能。\n\n首先，我来扩展我的\"个人档案\"和\"灵魂\"，然后建立知识库结构：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6jag6he6rls6_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/USER.md","newText":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:** 姚霖\n- **Feishu Open ID:** ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\n- **What to call them:** 姚霖\n- **Occupation:** 培训部,行政部,营销部,产品部,服务部\n- **Base Location:** 山东省青岛市市北区辽宁路147号QDF428\n- **Feishu Application Owner ID:** ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai (中国北京时间)\n- **Wechat:** _(待补充)_\n\n## 工作相关\n\n- **常用工具:** 飞书 (主要办公平台)、多维表格\n- **工作风格:** 喜欢自动化、效率工具，重视实际效果\n- **沟通偏好:** 直接、高效，不喜欢废话\n\n## 个人偏好\n\n- **性格:** 务实、直接\n- **偏好:** \n  - 喜欢有条理、有结构的信息\n  - 重视效率和自动化\n  - 喜欢学习新工具、新技能\n- **厌恶:** \n  - 重复性劳动\n  - 繁琐的手工操作\n\n## 学习记录\n\n- **2026-03-13:** 学习飞书妙搭一键部署 OpenClaw 教程\n- **2026-03-13:** 学习\"高手方法论\"知识库（时安、小龙虾等）\n- **2026-03-13:** 掌握核心技能：记忆系统、心跳系统、技能组合、深度进化、知识库管理\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.","oldText":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:** 姚霖\n- **Feishu Open ID:** ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\n- **What to c